HEADWORD: Stageplayer
<hw>Stage"play`er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An actor
on the stage; one whose occupation is to represent characters on the
stage; <as>as, <person>Garrick was</person> a celebrated
<ex>stageplayer</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

